00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:24.760
see on the street, a
wonderful human gesture.

00:18:24.760 --> 00:18:26.890
Scientific
philanthropy is to try

00:18:26.890 --> 00:18:30.520
to figure out why there are
so many people on the streets

00:18:30.520 --> 00:18:35.230
