00:30:43.760 --> 00:30:44.760
SUSAN ROCKEFELLER: Sure.

00:30:44.760 --> 00:30:47.780
So one that actually
has Google at its source

00:30:47.780 --> 00:30:49.970
is something called
Global Fishing Watch.

00:30:49.970 --> 00:30:51.620
So here we go.

00:30:51.620 --> 00:30:52.340
There's a slide.

00:30:52.340 --> 00:30:58.350
So Global Fishing
Watch was basically

00:30:58.350 --> 00:31:03.300
created with Oceana,
SkyTruth, and Google,

00:31:03.300 --> 00:31:06.780
and primarily funded through the
Leonardo DiCaprio Foundation.

00:31:06.780 --> 00:31:09.950
He was one of the lead
transformational funders

00:31:09.950 --> 00:31:10.450
for this.

00:31:10.450 --> 00:31:12.450
So we are very grateful to him.

00:31:12.450 --> 00:31:17.460
And what it does is it
allows, in almost real time,

00:31:17.460 --> 00:31:19.620
surveillance of
global fishing vessels

00:31:19.620 --> 00:31:22.280
so that you can help with--

00:31:22.280 --> 00:31:25.260
and anyone, NGOs,
governments, activists

00:31:25.260 --> 00:31:29.760
can look and see if vessels
are in illegal waters,

00:31:29.760 --> 00:31:32.430
so that it will help
with transparency,

00:31:32.430 --> 00:31:37.470
with IUU, illegal, unreported,
and unregulated fishing.

00:31:37.470 --> 00:31:40.230
So it is just a game changer.

00:31:40.230 --> 00:31:43.720
And our goal is to really
bring it to global scale.

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:48.240
So I think technology plays a
huge role in the surveillance

00:31:48.240 --> 00:31:50.850
aspect, especially if
you don't have funding

00:31:50.850 --> 00:31:54.576
for enforcement on the ocean.

00:31:54.576 --> 00:31:57.075
DAVID ROCKEFELLER JR: You can't
really have a police force--

00:31:57.075 --> 00:31:57.960
SUSAN ROCKEFELLER:
You can't police them.

00:31:57.960 --> 00:31:59.793
DAVID ROCKEFELLER JR:
--on the entire ocean,

00:31:59.793 --> 00:32:01.770
which covers more
than 70% of the globe.

00:32:01.770 --> 00:32:04.260
And so this is a way,
instead of having

00:32:04.260 --> 00:32:07.697
a vast set of police
boats out there

00:32:07.697 --> 00:32:09.030
that you have this surveillance.

00:32:09.030 --> 00:32:12.520
So if a ship--

00:32:12.520 --> 00:32:14.670
and mainly, we're focused
on large fishing boats--

00:32:14.670 --> 00:32:16.380
SUSAN ROCKEFELLER: Large
industrial fishing vessels.

00:32:16.380 --> 00:32:18.755
DAVID ROCKEFELLER JR: --is
either in an area it shouldn't

00:32:18.755 --> 00:32:22.770
be, as in a marine protected
area, or taking stocks

00:32:22.770 --> 00:32:28.320
that it's not licensed to take,
the surveillance catches them.

00:32:28.320 --> 00:32:32.781
And they can be punished,
