00:35:14.705 --> 00:35:17.190
DAVID ROCKEFELLER JR:
Do you want to start?

00:35:17.190 --> 00:35:18.530
SUSAN ROCKEFELLER: Sure.

00:35:18.530 --> 00:35:22.130
