different in that there

00:47:50.090 --> 00:47:54.140
was a real
responsibility that came

00:47:54.140 --> 00:47:57.500
with the privilege of
having the sale, which was,

00:47:57.500 --> 00:47:59.840
we had to make this money.

00:47:59.840 --> 00:48:04.790
The money had already been
organized by Mr. and Mrs.

00:48:04.790 --> 00:48:06.530
Rockefeller.

