you get a sale like this,

00:48:11.810 --> 00:48:13.310
you can taste it
almost immediately,

00:48:13.310 --> 00:48:16.250
that it's going to be a success.

00:48:16.250 --> 00:48:18.630
You know there's a buzz
that begins to build.

00:48:18.630 --> 00:48:21.260
And it may begin with
six of us sitting

00:48:21.260 --> 00:48:23.420
in an office talking about it.

00:48:23.420 --> 00:48:27.680
And then the whole company
took hold of what was going on

00:48:27.680 --> 00:48:29.094
