see how much more we could

00:48:45.380 --> 00:48:47.690
raise than the required funds.

00:48:47.690 --> 00:48:51.320
How much was what we
were doing individually

00:48:51.320 --> 00:48:55.280
contributing to
raising yet more,

00:48:55.280 --> 00:49:00.440
an additional, well,
almost $200 million

00:49:00.440 --> 00:49:04.370
that will go to the charities,
